{
  "name": "DataTable",
  "summary": "<p>使用 <strong>DataTable</strong> 属性可返回 <strong>DataTable</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例向嵌入式图表中添加带有外边框的模拟运算表。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasDataTable</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderOutline</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将图表工作表 Chart1 中图表的模拟运算表中的边框和字体设置为蓝色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表一张图表模拟运算表。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n\t<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t} <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n\t\t<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n\t}\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Border",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Border</strong>对象，它代表对象的边框。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 中第一张图表的模拟运算表的边框线条样式设置为虚线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">LineStyle</span> = xlDash\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例为图表工作表 Chart1 中图表添加模拟运算表，并将该运算表边框设置为红色的细线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasDataTable</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Border</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Weight</span> = xlHairline\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Border",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Font",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Font</strong> 对象，它代表指定对象的字体。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 中第一张图表的模拟运算表中的字体设置为蓝色粗体。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorIndex</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将图表工作表 Chart1 中图表的模拟运算表中的字体设置为加粗和倾斜，并将字体字号设置为 12 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">FontStyle</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Bold Italic&quot;</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Size</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">12</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Font",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Format",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回 <strong>ChartFormat</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将图表工作表 Chart1 中图表的模拟运算表的前景色设置为青色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将工作表 Sheet1 中第一张图表的模拟运算表的线条设置为红色的点划线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Sheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DashStyle</span> = msoLineDashDot\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Format</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Line</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ForeColor</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">RGB</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "ChartFormat",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "HasBorderHorizontal",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果图表模拟运算表具有水平单元格边框，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例使嵌入图表模拟运算表显示时带有外边框，但无单元格边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasDataTable</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderHorizontal</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderVertical</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderOutline</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示图表工作表 Chart1 中图表的模拟运算表是否具有水平单元格边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderHorizontal</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "HasBorderOutline",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果图表模拟运算表具有外部边框，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例使嵌入图表模拟运算表显示时带有外边框，但无单元格边框。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> chart = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>\n    chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasDataTable</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = chart.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderHorizontal</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderVertical</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n    datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderOutline</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断图表工作表 Chart1 中图表的模拟运算表是否具有外部边框，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> datatable = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">DataTable</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (datatable.<span class=\"hljs-property\">HasBorderOutline</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;图表模拟运算表具有外部边框&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;图表模拟运算表不具有外部边框&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
